import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

const layoutProps = {
  
};
export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"change-log"}}>{`Change Log`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
See `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://conventionalcommits.org"}}>{`Conventional Commits`}</MDXTag>{` for commit guidelines.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"8130-2019-03-20"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/compare/v8.12.0...v8.13.0"}}>{`8.13.0`}</MDXTag>{` (2019-03-20)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`Note:`}</MDXTag>{` Version bump only for package @sprucelabs/spruce-utils`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"8120-2019-02-27"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/compare/v8.11.0...v8.12.0"}}>{`8.12.0`}</MDXTag>{` (2019-02-27)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="p">{`Note:`}</MDXTag>{` Version bump only for package @sprucelabs/spruce-utils`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"8110-2019-02-19"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/compare/v8.10.1...v8.11.0"}}>{`8.11.0`}</MDXTag>{` (2019-02-19)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"bug-fixes"}}>{`Bug Fixes`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`graphql:`}</MDXTag>{` Add extensions back to non-subscription client (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/6fa47cf"}}>{`6fa47cf`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`graphql:`}</MDXTag>{` Include websocket dependency (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/4e355b1"}}>{`4e355b1`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`utils/graphql:`}</MDXTag>{` Add stub for global logs to pass lint (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/556c627"}}>{`556c627`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Add .editorconfigs targetting all files (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/dd2bfa3"}}>{`dd2bfa3`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Disable warning for fragments of the same name (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/c030cbf"}}>{`c030cbf`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`GraphQL `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`mutate`}</MDXTag>{` method name should match apollo equivalent method (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/2a4e263"}}>{`2a4e263`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Handle operationType -> clientMethod mapping, exceptions (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/12b1d1f"}}>{`12b1d1f`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"features"}}>{`Features`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`integrate gql client (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/4cb714f"}}>{`4cb714f`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`errors:`}</MDXTag>{` Make SpruceWebError configurable (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/f340add"}}>{`f340add`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`setToken for gql so auth does not need to be passed with each request (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/f33be7b"}}>{`f33be7b`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`subscriptions from skill to external graphql server (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/7524b32"}}>{`7524b32`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`graphql:`}</MDXTag>{` Improve logging data and messaging (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/aa6a6e1"}}>{`aa6a6e1`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`spruce-skill:`}</MDXTag>{` Support Skill View Dialogs in Core (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/8516ad0"}}>{`8516ad0`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="strong" components={components} parentName="li">{`utils:`}</MDXTag>{` Add iframe messaging tools (`}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/workspace.sprucebot-skills-kit/commit/f875811"}}>{`f875811`}</MDXTag>{`)`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
MDXContent.isMDXComponent = true
